==Starting off==
* '''Player:''' Hello, you look a bit worse for wear, are you okay?
* '''Holly:''' We're okay just very tired, our boss has been working us very hard this year.
* '''Player:''' Working hard on what?
* '''Holly:''' We work in a factory making Christmas presents, we used to love our work but this year our boss has turned into a corporate machine and is making us work crazy hours.
* '''Player:''' If you job is that bad can't you just quit?
* '''Holly:''' If we don't make presents it will ruin Christmas! We just need a better boss.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Perhaps I should speak to your boss.}}
** '''Player:''' Perhaps I should speak to your boss and teach her a thing or two about management.
** '''Holly:''' That would be great! We're based on a mountain to the far west of here but you can teleport there with us.
** '''Holly:''' Would you like to teleport to the factory now?
** {{tselect|Teleport to the Christmas Factory?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** {{qact|The player is teleported to the Christmas Factory.}}
** {{topt|No}}
*** {{tmissing}}
* {{topt|You'd better get back to work then!}}
** {{tmissing}}

